    <name>IdeaVim</name>
    <id>IdeaVIM</id>
    <description>
        <p>Vim emulation plug-in for IDEs based on the IntelliJ platform.</p>
        <p>IdeaVim supports many Vim features including normal/insert/visual modes, motion keys, deletion/changing,
            marks, registers, some Ex commands, Vim regexps, configuration via ~/.ideavimrc, macros, window commands,
            etc.
        </p>
        <p>See also:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/JetBrains/ideavim" rel="nofollow">GitHub repository</a>: documentation and
                contributing
            </li>
            <li><a href="http://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issues/VIM" rel="nofollow">Issue tracker</a>: feature requests
                and bug reports
            </li>
        </ul>
    </description>
